{"tid":1398220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[替代fb live] 發夢App試用後感（只限IOS）- Parachute","createTime":"2019-08-02T17:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T14:38:17.000Z","uid":215794,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"38abc4f1206a7740bef6ac1e4f05e756981ca902","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:23:37.000Z","msg":"今早有巴打出過post（但係好快就沉咗）<br />\n<br />\n[保護義士/前線/自己！！]一click秘密錄音+錄影+定位+通知聯絡人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1393409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1393409</a><br />\n<br />\n𠵱個App親身試過 唔算極之有用（尤其當有狗知道有𠵱隻App存在） <br />\n但可以考慮用嚟<span style=\"color: red;\">替代facebook live</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.guidingtech.com/media/assets/WordPress-Import/2016/05/parachute-safetrek-patronus-find-my-friends-iphone-app-safety-6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.guidingtech.com%2Fmedia%2Fassets%2FWordPress-Import%2F2016%2F05%2Fparachute-safetrek-patronus-find-my-friends-iphone-app-safety-6.png&h=34c1473c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介：<br />\n𠵱個App同fb live類似<br />\n都係可以拍片<br />\n就算俾狗拉咗 沒收咗你電話 都阻唔到段片公開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為係live stream上網嘅（只限Premium）<br />\n<br />\n本身隻App要買會員先可以live stream<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係</span><br />\n聽講佢哋個CEO已經表明支持香港人今次嘅運動<br />\n喺隻App入面亦都整咗個Session<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係畀香港人一鍵免費攞Premium Account</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: green;\">啟動方便</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以加<span style=\"color: red;\">Siri Add-on</span>  <br />\n簡單到 你開Siri 一叫「救命啊」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就可以即刻開到App+Activate Camera<br />\n<br />\n2. 有定位服務<br />\n<br />\n3. 你一Activate就會話畀你嘅緊急聯絡人知<br />\n亦都只係得你預先set咗嘅緊急聯終人先知<br />\n佢會喺個Web page度睇到<br />\n你拍嘅片 你嘅位置<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 只有IOS <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 去咗background / Sleep咗部機 會拍唔到片+錄唔到音 (但相信定位服務仍在)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    <span style=\"color: red;\">段片係唔會斷到</span> 只係你睇返段片 會話𠵱段時間係Interrupted<br />\n<br />\n3. 你network唔好（現場未必好）<br />\n又畀人強行熄機嘅話<br />\n可能只有部分片段先會上到Cloud<br />\n其它片段會留返喺部電話入面<br />\n<br />\n頭盔：<br />\n唔100%肯定 段片上咗去佢個Web service之後<br />\n會唔會完全保密 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家可以試吓<br />\n或者喺度討論吓"},{"pid":"d956d95ad14770acddfd9b62921ca61c91faf2e7","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"Siri啟動 Setting：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kr5C7Dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKr5C7Dc.png&h=681febfd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdNaJbx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdNaJbx.png&h=bcd703e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7d946c6093e0d8003acdc6e49fc6cd034eed6d3","tid":1398220,"uid":255578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:30:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66a1c5f4c265c2dd2035cbe23af9a391bb681cf6","tid":1398220,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f92423066173976551817bc53e719095daa1f1d","tid":1398220,"uid":255578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6cef8b757cddd89472ded5118af6267fbd74984","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:46:58.000Z","msg":"就算唔係發夢用都好<br />\n宜家治安咁差<br />\n例如女仔唔小心上錯賊車/賊屋<br />\n難保唔會救你一命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a91593afe5b3bbb805970a3b0495b8313b60e3","tid":1398220,"uid":124975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3538fac7ced04953bcffcd6bb819804dcd90b80c","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"起身一推<br />\n<br />\n85我要罷工"},{"pid":"0ae6df0a1fefd08283649f20e408e294d8f55607","tid":1398220,"uid":256846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:13:36.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打繼續推推推"},{"pid":"f97ff7d367e6b6510d8ccd06417d5ec7e1114f1c","tid":1398220,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:19:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6edb845e40023a500f8aaca2cbc11ea8461721b","tid":1398220,"uid":33325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"試下先thx"},{"pid":"383610ac0c2043adea317cf1f34d730e39a3977b","tid":1398220,"uid":142630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:19:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cd6be0148a7f0f724958b05511cdde51d735e91","tid":1398220,"uid":113210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2becce2673ad9c29bb379bd617092faa2dd29159","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:10:47.000Z","msg":"主要用途係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 你即將被狗拉/圍 你可以開定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就可以錄到被狗拉嘅過程<br />\n又或者你偷偷哋錄佢哋音<br />\n直到佢哋發現<br />\n咁你嘅朋友就會即時知道發生咩事<br />\n同埋知道你位置<br />\n過程中你要開住隻App 唔可以Lock screen<br />\n<br />\n2. 當普通fb live用<br />\n相信會方便啲<br />\n<br />\n3.（Advance）俾唔同地方嘅 前線/哨 作視像溝通用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n受益於<br />\n即時通知 聯絡人（手足）功能+Siri快速啟動功能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個手足可以即刻睇到你嗰邊嘅情況（live）<br />\n掌握即時最新資訊<br />\n但未喺現場試過 好可能會受網速所限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得有用請幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b5c04f0d603707eba0b51afe6d535b9b13976e","tid":1398220,"uid":152334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0d4492a2b8ac8e21084fc2e7fc9db97e0922a18","tid":1398220,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T20:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e67f014b55c53270cc1971bf173ddfc04186c54","tid":1398220,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"想問下係咪冇android版<br />\nandroid有冇類似app"},{"pid":"55b8243eb5b67ef09f7dbce0c906396f50c356d9","tid":1398220,"uid":272353,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:59:19.000Z","msg":"我set救命呀 siri同我打999⋯⋯"},{"pid":"c6e01d7dfe8b71e1650867feeec00c6a053f4e64","tid":1398220,"uid":82121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"呢隻app可唔可靠，會唔會比資料狗隻"},{"pid":"9595117cee58d1a33338cefbbe97adce9213619c","tid":1398220,"uid":61517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09338b65dbc002d208c20920a41914a38e70fd80","tid":1398220,"uid":83989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5ccb9cfa5a67542d41e8b07df6089b84f470c04","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6e01d7dfe8b71e1650867feeec00c6a053f4e64","tid":1398220,"uid":82121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:49:53.000Z","msg":"呢隻app可唔可靠，會唔會比資料狗隻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"信佢好過信fuckbook<br />\n你信得過fb live就信埋佢啦"},{"pid":"d961a96a0fa9200babf7c332ba5aea7cc022873c","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e67f014b55c53270cc1971bf173ddfc04186c54","tid":1398220,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"想問下係咪冇android版<br />\nandroid有冇類似app"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"無android版<br />\n<br />\n唔知 但相信有都：<br />\n一係功能唔勁<br />\n二要收錢<br />\n<br />\nParachute每月收錢 本身唔平<br />\n但宜家係特別free畀香港人 支持我哋（credit to某位搵人哋CEO嘅巴打）"},{"pid":"c782c367b86365626c465d582d9e3b00e1ab39d1","tid":1398220,"uid":170967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"要開app先錄到？冇得鎖機用好危險喎，俾班狗搶走部機就乜資料都俾晒人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2966bae6d20d95d439e9d11b1a8ee7129a3eb343","tid":1398220,"uid":1103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e25e2570425e3f793aab272f2f1729b91b6058e","tid":1398220,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"69c95c40cd7f7cf84f499259f4f65eea2a06bc36","tid":1398220,"uid":215794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e25e2570425e3f793aab272f2f1729b91b6058e","tid":1398220,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T02:42:08.000Z","msg":"留明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T03:37:42.000Z","msg":"馬後炮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實喺831嘅太子站<br />\n𠵱隻App係好有用：<br />\n一、嗰陣唔多人 上網一定穩定<br />\n二、只有你嘅緊急聯絡人收到通知<br />\n唔會咁快將啲嘢通晒天（相比起用fuckbook）<br />\n可以等黑警講夠大話先踢爆佢哋<br />\n三、你嘅緊急聯絡人可以即刻睇到你嘅情況  知道你嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">位置</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a2cc34af719daf302cd55531ac0ba22da105aac","tid":1398220,"uid":117207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b8637cc5fdbf39a21c5c5fe1c720b36dac22851","tid":1398220,"uid":7326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0